snippet.title: Dead Secret Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Who killed Harris Bullard? Designed for console and VR, Dead Secret is a mystery thriller. Delve into a dead man’s bizarre past to solve the riddle of his death before you become the next victim. http://deadsecret.com

Available now for Gear VR, and coming soon to Steam, Oculus Rift, and PSN.
